PKM Management
API endpoints for managing PKM (Program Kreativitas Mahasiswa)



GET
/pkm
Get list of PKM


Returns paginated list of PKM with optional filters (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
search
string
(query)
Search by singkatan or nama

search
is_active
boolean
(query)
Filter by active status


--
per_page
integer
(query)
Items per page

Default value : 15

15
